# Frequently Asked Interview Questions

### Q1. Why do we use GROUP BY?

To group rows with the same values and perform aggregate calculations like COUNT, SUM, AVG, MIN, and MAX.

---

### Q2. Can HAVING be used without GROUP BY?

Yes.

```sql
SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM employee
HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
```

---

### Q3. Execution Order of SQL Query

```sql
FROM
WHERE
GROUP BY
HAVING
SELECT
ORDER BY
LIMIT
```

Very common interview question.

